dc_title_s: International local aeronautical map. Bihaār. N. G-45.
dc_description_s: Cartographic Details: Scale 1:1,000,000 ; Polyconic projection (E 84°--E 90°/N 28°--N 24°). Relief shown by gradient tints and spot heights. Shows emergency landing grounds, direction finding stations, roads, streams, railroads, towns, canals, marsh, steamer routes, and glaciers. Includes index to adjoining sheets, administrative index, and pronunciation guide. Dimensions: 44 x 59 centimeters
